#. module: account_payment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:account_payment.portal_invoice_payment
msgid ""
"<strong>No suitable payment option could be found.</strong><br/>\n"
"                                If you believe that it is an error, please contact the website administrator."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ບໍ່ພົບຕົວເລືອກການຊຳລະເງິນທີ່ເໝາະສົມ.</strong><br/>\n"
"                                ຫາກທ່ານຄິດວ່ານີ້ຄືຄວາມຜິດພາດ, ກະລຸນາຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ເບິ່ງແຍງລະບົບເວັບ"
"ໄຊ."

#. module: account_payment
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:account_payment.payment_refund_wizard_view_form
msgid ""
"<strong>Warning!</strong> There is a refund pending for this payment.\n"
"                        Wait a moment for it to be processed. If the refund is still pending in a\n"
"                        few minutes, please check your payment provider configuration."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄຳເຕືອນ!</strong> ມີການຄືນເງິນທີ່ກຳລັງລໍຖ້າດຳເນີນການສຳລັບການຊຳລະນີ້.\n"
"                        ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າຈັກຄູ່ເພື່ອໃຫ້ລະບົບປະມວນຜົນ. ຫາກການຄືນເງິນຍັງຄ້າງຢູ່\n"
"                        ໃນອີກບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດນາທີ, ກະລຸນາກວດສອບການຕັ້ງຄ່າຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ."

